<h2 id=3D"Saucedemo_TestCase-Module1:Login">Module 1: Login</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>Scenario ID</strong></p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>Tags</strong></p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>Scenario</strong></p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>Description (BDD Steps)</strong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>TC_LOGIN_001</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>@ui @smoke @positive</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Login successfully with standard user</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Given</strong> I am on the login page<br><strong>When</strong> I=
 enter username "standard_user" and password "secret_sauce"<br><strong>And<=
/strong> I click the Login button<br><strong>Then</strong> I should be redi=
rected to the inventory page<br><strong>And</strong> the product list shoul=
d be visible</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>TC_LOGIN_002</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>@ui @negative</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Login fails for locked out user</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Given</strong> I am on the login page<br><strong>When</strong> I=
 enter username "locked_out_user" and password "secret_sauce"<br><strong>An=
d</strong> I click the Login button<br><strong>Then</strong> an error messa=
ge "Epic sadface: Sorry, this user has been locked out." should appear</p><=
/td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>TC_LOGIN_003</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>@ui @negative</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Login with empty username shows error</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Given</strong> I am on the login page<br><strong>When</strong> I=
 leave the username field empty<br><strong>And</strong> I enter password "s=
ecret_sauce"<br><strong>And</strong> I click the Login button<br><strong>Th=
en</strong> an error message "Epic sadface: Username is required" should ap=
pear</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>TC_LOGIN_004</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>@ui @negative</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Login with empty password shows error</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Given</strong> I am on the login page<br><strong>When</strong> I=
 enter username "standard_user"<br><strong>And</strong> I leave the passwor=
d field empty<br><strong>And</strong> I click the Login button<br><strong>T=
hen</strong> an error message "Epic sadface: Password is required" should a=
ppear</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>TC_LOGIN_005</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>@ui @negative</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Login with invalid credentials shows error</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Given</strong> I am on the login page<br><strong>When</strong> I=
 enter username "invalid_user" and password "wrong_pass"<br><strong>And</st=
rong> I click the Login button<br><strong>Then</strong> an error message "E=
pic sadface: Username and password do not match" should appear</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>TC_LOGIN_006</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>@ui @positive</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Error message clears when X button is clicked</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Given</strong> I am on the login page<br><strong>When</strong> I=
 submit the form with empty credentials<br><strong>Then</strong> an error m=
essage should appear<br><strong>When</strong> I click the X button on the e=
rror message<br><strong>Then</strong> the error message should disappear</p=
></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>TC_LOGIN_007</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>@ui @performance</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Login with performance glitch user succeeds (slow)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Given</strong> I am on the login page<br><strong>When</strong> I=
 enter username "performance_glitch_user" and password "secret_sauce"<br><s=
trong>And</strong> I click the Login button<br><strong>Then</strong> I shou=
ld eventually be redirected to the inventory page (may take up to 10s)</p><=
/td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>TC_LOGIN_008</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>@ui @smoke @positive</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Logout successfully returns to login page</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Given</strong> I am logged in as "standard_user"<br><strong>When=
</strong> I open the burger menu<br><strong>And</strong> I click the Logout=
 button<br><strong>Then</strong> I should be redirected to the login page<b=
r><strong>And</strong> the Login button should be visible</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
